[gd_scene format=3]

; Placeholder wetland/region-signature prop (bootstrap-polygon art, matching the
; StandingStone/LoneTree/Bush/PineTree convention). Purely visual: no collision, no script.
; A small cluster of thin, tall vertical reed-blade silhouettes at a slight lean, plus a
; low sandy tuft base, so it reads as a lake-shore reed cluster at a glance. Colors from the
; locked shared palette (STYLE_GUIDE.md: forest_floor #216633 / grass_dark #288A36, with a
; sand #E7CD92 base to ground it in the shore). Authored from the node origin (base at y~0)
; upward so y_sort uses the base as the sort key, like the other props.

